{"tid":179923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本上班男搭電車「邊吃邊哭」","createTime":"2017-03-30T14:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T18:03:37.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39cd71783abad200d4a20bd8ab3223a0a5472031","tid":179923,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"近期網路流傳一則影片，有民眾拍下一位日本上班族回家的情況，只見他獨自搭著電車，手中抓著三明治猛吃，眼淚卻忍不這流下來，且表情相當煎熬、委屈，令人看了鼻酸，也讓網友想起電視劇《四重奏》知名台詞：「泣きながら、ご飯食べたことある人は、生きて行けます（會邊哭邊吃飯的人，能過活下去）」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pics.ctitv.com/wpimg/2017/03/192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpics.ctitv.com%2Fwpimg%2F2017%2F03%2F192.jpg&h=df4af6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bepo.ctitv.com.tw/2017/03/199176/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbepo.ctitv.com.tw%2F2017%2F03%2F199176%2F&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ba218ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bepo.ctitv.com.tw/2017/03/199176/</a>"},{"pid":"ad993d051cdfdd318bdbbe982b9d5bae89427123","tid":179923,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"面對工作卻是生不如死，全因日本上班族文化相當嚴苛、講求禮貌，任何事情都要和主管報告、連絡、相談，若有細節沒注意到，被潑水並不稀奇，這種心理上的折磨，比生理還痛苦<br />\n<br />\n其實連條友做乜喊都唔知，作都唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd256d0e5bb4fa0b0a98e607e7f311d9c060fb1","tid":179923,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127d7e5f8079aa9e45c8a6ac320a57e371d583bb","tid":179923,"uid":27609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"諗起郭富城食魚柳包喊"},{"pid":"00a5eb730be71f8b13f6c33f6798a62a16f0fa2f","tid":179923,"uid":19632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"屌好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\